Title: 155: How AI and Blockchain Converge
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with complexity scientist, Francesco Corea. You will hear what is a complexity scientist, learn the benefits of the intersection of AI and blockchain, and know the pros and cons of being knowledgeable in different fields like AI and blockchain.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/155
